  "texts": [
    "This study aims to assess the ability of open-source LLMs to accurately generate explanations within an RAG system like XpertAI as an alternative to proprietary LLMs.",
    "We generated explanations from these LLMs using the same molecular features and literature data employed in previous case studies.",
    "Then a human evaluator was asked to assess the accuracy of the generated explanations for all 5 case studies.",
    "The evaluator assigned a score of 1 for accurate explanations and 0 for inaccurate ones.",
    "The scores for references were averaged by the number of references in each explanation before totaling."
  ],
